long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is for teachers to generate links that automatically open in the Deledao Education app on student-used iPads issued by the school.  
 
Deledao is a digital wellness company. From filtering inappropriate content to detecting signs of cyberbullying and self-harm, Deledao protects students online. Deledao can only protect students using iPads when students use the Deledao Education app. 
 
Because iPads automatically launch webpages with Safari, teachers can download this extension to generate URLs that launch in the Deledao Education app instead. 
 
By installing the extension, you agree to Deledaoâ€™s terms and conditions (www.deledao.com/eula) and privacy policy (www.deledao.com/privacy).
